General.Name: Online Brands Nordic AB
General.Description: Online Brands Nordic AB (publ) engages in the online sale of carpets under Trendcarpet brand in Sweden and internationally. The company also sells hats online under Hatshop brand; kitchen utensils through online and its stores under Kitchenlab brand; underwear and T-shirts for men and women online under Bread & Boxers brand; and outdoor and ski clothing for children and youth under Isbjörn brand through retailers, and e-commerce channels and marketplaces. In addition, it operates a jewelry store under the Victorins brand name. The company is based in Hisings Backa, Sweden.
